Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:09.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not getting enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:15.12,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Pardon me. I wasn't able to sleep very well last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:19.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is there no charm for sleeping well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.96,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,There is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:25.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Charm for getting good sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:28.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Have someone give you a lap pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,With this, a peaceful slumber is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,...all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:35.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is not a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:37.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But it does sound like you could get a good sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:42.73,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I had my brother do it for me often when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.99,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,but now that I'm older...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:47.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:51.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How about having Tomoya-kun give you the lap pillow in place of your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:59.04,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I shouldn't. I would feel bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't worry. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:16.81,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Then I'll accept your offer and borrow him for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.15,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:31.03,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It feels... good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She fell asleep in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't feel anything looking at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:44.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To be honest, I am a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But when I see that look on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She must have been tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:55.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She must always be stressed over the fights Sudou-san and her friends get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yo ho! Is Yukine-chan here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let me have your delicious pilaf again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.07,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Making yourselves at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:07.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Hush please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.37,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Kazuto Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.42,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I completely fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.64,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,I'll let you use my lap next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.77,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,I want to meet Yukine Onee-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:11.69,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,Yuki-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.02,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Sudou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.82,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.82,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}A Courageous Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.65,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,They all think Sunohara-san is my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:25.41,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,Yeah. They think Kazuto-san got out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.17,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,They're all scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:38.00,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,They're afraid they have no chance of winning now that Miyazawa Kazuto's back on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:41.76,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,That's why they've panicked and have snuck over to our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.80,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,This was never supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But that's all a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was Tomoyo who beat them up them yesterday and-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.56,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Miyazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.35,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Regarding what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.19,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,Crap! I'll see you again, Yuki-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.94,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Sudou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.03,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Looks like I came at the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.50,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,So you guys got caught in another mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We didn't choose to be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:20.84,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,{\fscx107}It's all because you pretended to be Miyazawa Kazuto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I am familiar with the name Miyazawa Kazuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:30.47,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I heard a rumor back when I was still fighting gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:36.19,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It said Miyazawa Kazuto would be the only person who could fight me face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Face to face against you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:42.65,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I've heard many of your great stories, too, Sakagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:48.12,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I won't bring this matter up in school this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.95,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.45,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:56.21,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The other day, I had a chance to talk to\Na member of another school's Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.75,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,There have been many fights in this city recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:05.01,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,At this rate, we will see the police become involved, sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.47,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Here's my advice. {ep7}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:10.47,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Stop being fools and be friends. {ep7}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.81,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'll all suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.40,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Those bastards! I'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Let's go raid their place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.99,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We'll show them what we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.12,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa. When will your brother be discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:39.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kazuto-san can stop the fight, right? {ep7}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.46,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.38,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll go talk to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Miyazawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You guys stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hold up, Miyazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:04.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think about it. It's not like you can solve anything even if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:10.78,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm familiar to them, and I know where they hang out often, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your brother doesn't know what's going on? {ep7}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if he's in the hospital, can't he convince Sudou and the others over the phone? {ep7}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.22,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.68,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,So at this rate, both sides will be broken up, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:38.77,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Yes. If the fight escalates,\Nthe police may become involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,How do you expect us to back out now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:45.36,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\fs78.3}Since Miyazawa Kazuto's back on the streets,\Nwe have to take you guys down before we're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.94,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Like I said, that was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.57,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,How so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.82,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Last night, we got our asses kicked by your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was Sakagami Tomo-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:02.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yukine-san. We've got nothing against you, but we can't listen to you on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.50,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We've got injured people on our side, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.84,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We can't stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.42,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Stop it you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.76,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,This is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.13,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,We have to continue until one of us is crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.30,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Yeah! This is a fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.81,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.85,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,I said shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.40,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,You're all being rude to our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:30.36,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Yukine-san. You've treated my wounds before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:36.83,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten the care\Nand the taste of the pilaf from that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:40.25,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,It's been a month, and he hasn't taken off the bandage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:43.50,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sasaki-san likes girls who are good cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.04,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.13,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,No, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:52.76,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,But as you see, we can't let things end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.76,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,So, how does a one-on-one between the leaders sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.39,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,One-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.56,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Your brother and I will fight one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.15,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Whoever loses will submit to the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.77,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,That's the limit to the compromise we can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.11,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,And you agreed to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.41,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Yuki-nee, how could you do that without talking to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.71,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That was the only choice I had in the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The time is tomorrow evening, at the river bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.88,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,But Kazuto-san can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.09,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,We have to send a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.93,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But will they agree to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:42.77,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Hey. They think Sunohara-san's Miyazawa Kazuto-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,That's right!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.35,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.98,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Please wait! Sunohara-san has nothing to do with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:56.61,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,You were bragging yesterday that it was you who busted up four guys at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.41,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,Four at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.20,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.58,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You'll totally do as Kazuto-san's substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:07.37,Default,Sis,0,0,0,,They often say "Don't judge a book by its cover", but wow, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sunohara Aniki! Please lend us your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Can I get another glass of this first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:28.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san. Will you really be doing a one-on-one fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't think fighting is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.74,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.16,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,They aren't that bad of people, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:47.96,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,But when there are two groups in\Na small city, they can't help but clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:57.01,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Unless everyone in the city is happy,\Nno one is truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.56,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,They're all nice people individually,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:06.10,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,yet, why does this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Man, this is pretty nerve-wracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.66,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you still going to make us wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.33,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wait until Sasaki-san comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.50,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,God, it feels like my heart's going to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:32.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san. How about filling\Nyour stomach while you have the chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is a little something from my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.92,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,From Sanae-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:42.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,{\fs78.3}I said Sunohara-san would be having\Na very important fight, and so she made me bring this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Her newest creation. Hyper Rainbow Bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And a message from Dad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He said, "Rainbow to you".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:57.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And here's an ultimate jam made by her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you put this ultimate jam on Mom's bread,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,you've got yourself the ultimate combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Would you all like to try some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.66,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,We can?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.25,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.83,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.47,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Please get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.63,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.39,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,What do we do? Everyone's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.90,Default,Sis,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We don't have time to argue. Take care of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.99,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.74,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's been a little misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's actually not Miyazawa Kazuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you'll have to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:59.59,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,It's no good. We need the real Miyazawa Kazuto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.97,Default,Sis,0,0,0,,Your brother won't come no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:08.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To either fight Sasaki-san or stop the fight, we need Miyazawa-san's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:16.23,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll play with you a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.03,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Go, Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:27.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.33,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.84,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Do you have a bad right shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I don't need you to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.97,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.35,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,You're one tough guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.90,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Enough. Stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.48,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Looks like your boys are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.41,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.88,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,What did you do to Yuki-nee's bud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.09,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Everyone, follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sunohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.76,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Sasaki-san's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.97,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.05,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.77,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.82,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,K-Kazuto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.61,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.70,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.53,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,So that's the real Miyazawa Kazuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.74,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,He snuck out of the hospital, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.16,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,As the rumors say, you've got balls, Miyazawa Kazuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:24.04,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,But I can't go easy on you.\NSorry, but I've got to beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:32.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.68,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.52,Default,Sas,0,0,0,,Stop it. What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.36,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.90,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm Miyazawa Kazuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop it, Miyazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.24,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,When did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:58.24,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,She went running, saying she'd go get her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.25,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,I thought she went to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.37,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,There's no way she can go get him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.84,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,There's no way she can go get Kazuto-san!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.34,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Let go!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.84,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.47,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yuki-nee, it's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.18,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,Yuki-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.06,Default,Sud,0,0,0,,Why is she doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:29.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To stop you guys, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The only way to stop the fight is for Miyazawa Kazuto to come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's why she pretended to be her brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:44.79,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Why... Why do we have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.13,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,What does it take to not fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.42,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,What does it... What does it take...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:18:00.39,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,Please. Please stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:06.40,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,I'm sure my brother wishes for that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So that was the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:29.58,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,For the longest time, I was afraid of my brother and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:38.76,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,But seeing Sudou-san and Tajima-san cry at his funeral, I wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:45.10,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,"Why didn't I try to understand his way of life more?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:50.69,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,That's why I mustered up some courage to get to know everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.82,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,At first, it was scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:59.70,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,but little by little, you all let me into the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:07.46,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,And being with you all made me feel like I was laughing with Kazuto Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:13.21,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,My brother wished there were no fights until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:19.22,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,{\fs78.3}But if the truth of him missing were to be revealed,\Nwe thought Sasaki-san's group would come against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:25.85,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,That's why we talked matters over and\Ndecided to keep my brother's death a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.90,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,It was my brother's wish to be rid of fights from this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.53,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,I wanted to realize that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.28,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.85,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kazuto Nii-san's happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.96,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I feel at peace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:38.59,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It could be that I've finally accepted what happened to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:43.47,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I owe it to all of you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:50.14,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Are you all familiar with this city's legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:55.94,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,The moment something good happens or a moment of happiness is experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.28,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,an orb of light appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.86,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,No one knows what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:06.49,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,What is for certain is those lights are taken as symbols of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:11.00,Default,Miy,0,0,0,,And if you obtain one, any one wish can be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. Isn't this Misae-san's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:15.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:19.96,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,But it looks like less and less people see them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.01,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So the light Okazaki says he saw is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:28.81,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Maybe Okazaki-san is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:29.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.52,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm not sure of anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.73,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,But Okazaki-san, you're still you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.90,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,My important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:46.28,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,You're all my important friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:52.00,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm really a blessed person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.00,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm supported by so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.38,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Kazuto Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.59,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.35,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(981.818,452.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What will you do once you graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:49.52,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You've got a really gloomy face so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:52.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Did you have a fight with Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:55.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Something similar happened before, too, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:58.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I mean, at crucial times, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:01.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I hope it took his mind off things a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:23:59.53,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:02.58,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:06.21,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun isn't happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.35,0:24:09.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,384.75)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Episode 9
